Steps to delete your account
If you wish to unsubscribe and delete your data from our platform, follow these steps:

Write an email: From the email address associated with your account, write to [devgoderstudiossupp@gmail.com].

Subject: In the subject line, write: "Account deletion request."

Body of the message: For security reasons, please confirm your desire to permanently delete your account. This is not mandatory, but knowing the reason would greatly help us to continue improving.

Wait for confirmation: Once we receive your email, our team will process your request.

Important information:
Response time: Deletion will be completed within a maximum of 7 business days.

Scope: Deleting your account will permanently erase your progress logs, personal data, and any saved settings. This action cannot be undone.
